Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用我的方式战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs56\fad(500,800)\pos(960,1069)}一个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来摆脱第二月球的追兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝也完好无损的到手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么值得担心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹是亲儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了维甘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又能怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么扔下我和妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论有什么理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不回来让我们放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是伊泽尔坎特侵略地球的真正目的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他说要选出优秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们移居地球 建立伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他简直是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他说这是拯救人类的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球和维甘的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经走到无可挽回的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在只有做力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守护自己最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 要记得好好刷牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再也见不到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐接下来要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小优
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们3个也要保重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 温蒂也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴洛诺克 按计划抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤诺亚姑姑 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3个月没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 姑姑担心死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该先跟这个人说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 你这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13年不见了…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得和骨架一起换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则不可能修成原来那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没打算把它修成原来那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接进化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进化成新的高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你为什么要去当宇宙海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言难尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13年前 在战斗中身负重伤的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被宇宙海盗救起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养伤期间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一起和海盗们共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的生活让我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争中隐藏的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指信息胶囊里提到的EXA-DB吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是不仅限于此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军的腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有迫使维甘走上战争之路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星圈的残酷现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从得知这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法单纯地把维甘视为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就想去当置身事外的海盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 我找到了适合我的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫适合你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在为保护大家而战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 站在一方的立场攻击对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后真的能守护心爱的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 战斗是无法避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果让两者的力量趋于均衡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走维甘和联邦军执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所需的重要战略物资和情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止大规模战斗的爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我作为海盗力所能及的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要地球和维甘的实力均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争就会陷入胶着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有大量的牺牲者出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够让吉欧和罗玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所爱的那些人享受和平的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是痴人说梦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天不扑灭那些杀戮成性的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一天没有和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有在这场战争中胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把维甘斩草除根一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道您会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法和父亲不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用我的方式去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 我现在得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还会见面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你身体无恙就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要做这么全面的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不了解他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难保不会在你身体上做什么手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还须检查是否受到火星疫病的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘可能不像爷爷说得那样 都是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论出于什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们夺走了我们许多最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星圈的人们也有苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让战争早日结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…到底被他们灌输了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的相信这是维甘奇怪行动的原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以战争为借口 选出所谓优秀人种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把弱小者逐渐淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目的无非是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只以消灭对方为目的的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是正确的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论究竟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特是个疯狂的独裁者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他指挥下的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了是可憎的敌国以外什么都不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次作战的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回月面上遗留的原联邦基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月神基地曾经是联邦在月面的一大据点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在联邦主力被大量遣往地球支援的间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不慎落入敌手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月神基地司令官 阿隆·西蒙斯叛变投敌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时有相当数量的间谍渗透进入基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在维甘发起攻击的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地内的潜伏人员发动叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦的兵力几乎全军覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的月球基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被敌人利用作为进攻地球的补给站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我们曾接到命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让歌姬号前往月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想来这可能也是敌人的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为阻止维甘进一步威胁地球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决定将夺回月神基地的作战计划付诸实施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西想给我看？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高达吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据AGE-3在火星圈的战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE系统设计出的新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了实现前所未有的高速移动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体进行了大幅轻量化改造
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 还追加了X-Rounder专用小型支援部件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 最新型的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-FX
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-FX？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FX即是 X-Rounder辅助型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门为跟上X-Rounder的战斗能力而设计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以把它简单理解成最强机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台高达的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以精确瞄准敌人机动战士的某个部分吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然取决于机师的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但机体确实有这种潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是和你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:15:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能够实现我想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快和敌人接火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 高达
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…到底想把我怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出求救信号 等候营救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用我的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近月面 准备着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C浮游炮 展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人也是人 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我会坚持我战斗的方式直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 准备等离子潜航导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次出击 我心里一直有个疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被禁止使用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁同意搭载它们上船的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这征得了艾伦格雷亚斯总司令的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那东西的威力太大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 您打算把基地一起毁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野老司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是遵从章程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心存疑问的话可以去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要亲手歼灭维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到一个不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运动过于单调会被吃透的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月神基地上出现高热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人高热源反应 消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在正要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是无谋 鲁莽的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有多少成功的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会陪着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再需要隐藏身份的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就不再需要自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 真打算不杀敌人结束战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙儿 离月面着陆不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持警惕上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长 即将进入月球战斗空域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 这到底是吹得哪阵风？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月神基地如果不能重回联邦之手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者的均衡就会被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘会源源不绝地向地球圈输送兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是多么庞大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望是我杞人忧天
